<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shí zì jià 迦南544</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shí zì jià, shí zì jià, gǔ jiù de shí zì jià,
 zhǔ yé sū, bèi zhe tā, shàng gè gè tā huí tiān jiā.
 wǒ yě yào bèi shàng tā, rì yè zǒu huí tiān jiā,
 zǒu dào nǎ, fēng yǔ dǎ, wǒ hái shì yào bèi shàng tā.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>544</hymn_number>
</song>